        filter = f"{name}"
        if params:
            filter = f"{name}/{params.replace(', ', '/')}"
        out = subprocess.check_output([benchmark, f"--benchmark_filter={filter}", "--benchmark_format=json"])
    
        import json
        out = json.loads(out)
    
        assert(len(out["benchmarks"]) == 1)

        unit = out["benchmarks"][0]["time_unit"]
    
        if unit == "s":
            time *= 1000
            unit = "ms"
        if unit == "ms":
            time *= 1000
            unit = "us"
        if unit == "us":
            time *= 1000
            unit = "ns"
    
        assert(unit == "ns")
    
        return time
